data.description: Walkability is great. But why not add drive, ride, cycle, and paddle. Here you can! Trail Walk Condos sit near the end of Lake Washington with the Sammamish Slough right outside your door. Parks like new TI'awh-ah-dees, Logboom, Wayne, and Rhododendrum are all accesible via the Burke Gilman Trail just steps away. Lets not stop there! Food, drink, and entertainment are also a short walk. OK, but what about the condo? At Trail Walk you have an outdoor pool, clubhouse with exercise room within these well-manicured grounds. Inside 1174 sq ft, 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, wood floors, fireplace awaits you. And 2 parking spots! With Bellevue and Seattle a short ride or drive away, all your bases are covered. Great HOA. Come take a look for yourself
